	(25, 2, 'SxKJ-CoC-Ms', 'EWTN - Easter Stewardship Message', 'ewtn-easter-stewardship-message', 'At EWTN, we want to inspire you during this special Easter season. So, we invite you to sign up for the free eBook, Our Risen Lord: Reflections on the Resurrection, Divine Mercy, and Pentecost, featuring insights from popes, saints, and other holy men and women.\r\nYou help make this Network possible with your prayers and support, so this is a token of our sincere gratitude. \r\nFor your FREE eBook, please scan the QR code or visit ewtn.com/easter2026. May God bless you this Easter and always.\n\nSubscribe to EWTN’s YouTube Channel: https://bit.ly/3hBbdVX\n\nEWTN Global Catholic Network, in its 40th year, is the largest religious media network in the world and was founded by Mother Mary Angelica, PCPA. The Daily Televised Mass is broadcast live 7 days a week at 7:00 a.m CST (watch it here: https://www.ewtn.com/tv/watch-live). The Mass is uploaded to YouTube every day along with many other programs. To contact EWTN, send an email to our Viewer Services team at viewer@ewtn.com or call 1-800-447-3986.\n\nTo learn more about EWTN please visit https://www.ewtn.com\nDonate now - https://bit.ly/3pBGjRU\nFollow us on Facebook - https://www.facebook.com/ewtnonline\nFollow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/EWTN\nFollow us on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/ewtnmedia/', 'https://i.ytimg.com/vi/SxKJ-CoC-Ms/hqdefault.jpg', '2026-03-29 03:00:16', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SxKJ-CoC-Ms', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/SxKJ-CoC-Ms', 'PT1M1S', 374, 0, 0, '{"id": "SxKJ-CoC-Ms", "etag": "pa8o3UXkomRECPfisF7Gpf_cYMo", "kind": "youtube#video", "snippet": {"tags": ["promo", "promo-8417bf1b4ee6740a"], "title": "EWTN - Easter Stewardship Message", "channelId": "UCijDos-LUTh9RQvSCMQqN6Q", "localized": {"title": "EWTN - Easter Stewardship Message", "description": "At EWTN, we want to inspire you during this special Easter season. So, we invite you to sign up for the free eBook, Our Ri