	(35, 2, 'HnrnliBuMOU', 'Gospel According to Bas Rutten Trailer', 'gospel-according-to-bas-rutten-trailer', 'Is the Gospel just ancient history - or is it alive today?\nIn the premiere episode of Gospel According To, UFC Hall of Famer Bas Rutten shares his powerful testimony - from bullied kid in the Netherlands to becoming one of the most feared fighters in MMA history.\nThis is not just a sports story.\nIt’s a story about fear.\nIdentity.\nAddiction.\nSuccess that doesn’t satisfy.\nAnd the moment everything changed.\nAfter rising to become the “Baddest Man on the Planet” in Pancrase and the UFC, Bas faced something he couldn’t fight in the ring: loss of identity, injury, and personal collapse.\nThrough an unexpected friendship and a radical encounter with Jesus Christ, Bas discovered the only power strong enough to defeat fear.\nThis is the Gospel according to Bas Rutten.\nAnd it’s just the beginning.\n\n#BasRutten #UFC #ChristianTestimony #FaithStory #MMA #JesusChrist #Gospel #EWTN #ConversionStory #Documentary #FaithInCulture', 'https://i.ytimg.com/vi/HnrnliBuMOU/maxresdefault.jpg', '2026-03-26 12:00:35', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HnrnliBuMOU', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/HnrnliBuMOU', 'PT1M6S', 3376, 0, 10, '{"id": "HnrnliBuMOU", "etag": "y9bkpoBKizxqPQjXS5RbISx10K8", "kind": "youtube#video", "snippet": {"tags": ["bas rutten", "bas rutten faith", "bas rutten catholic", "conversion story", "documentary", "catholic documentary", "catholic conversion", "catholic celebrities", "catholic celebrity", "catholic athletes", "christian celebrities", "christian athletes", "jesus", "catholic conversion story", "jesus testimony", "ewtn media", "ewtn studios", "catholic", "convert to catholicism"], "title": "Gospel According to Bas Rutten Trailer", "channelId": "UCijDos-LUTh9RQvSCMQqN6Q", "localized": {"title": "Gospel According to Bas Rutten Trailer", "description": "Is the Gospel just ancient history - or is it alive today?\\nIn the premiere episode of Gospel According To, UFC Hall of Famer Bas Rutten shares his powerful testimony - from bullied kid in the Netherlands to becoming one of the most feared fighters in MMA history.\\nThis is not just a sports story.\\nIt’s a story about fear.\\nIdentity.\\nAddiction.\\nSuccess that doesn’t satisfy.\\nAnd the moment everything changed.\\nAfter rising to become the “Baddest Man on the Planet” in Pancrase and the UFC, Bas faced something he couldn’t fight in the ring: loss of identity, injury, and personal collapse.\\nThrough an unexpected friendship and a radical encounter with Jesus Christ, Bas discovered the only power strong enough to defeat fear.\\nThis is the Gospel according to Bas Rutten.\\nAnd it’s just the beginning.\\n\\n#BasRutten #UFC #ChristianTestimony #FaithStory #MMA #JesusChrist #Gospel #EWTN #ConversionStory #Documentary #FaithInCulture"}, "categoryId": "27", "thumbnails": {"high": {"url": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi/HnrnliBuMOU/hqdefault.jpg", "width": 480, "height": 360}, "maxres": {"url": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi/HnrnliBuMOU/maxresdefault.jpg", "width": 1280, "height": 720}, "medium": {"url": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi/HnrnliBuMOU/mqdefault.jpg", "width": 320, "height": 180}, "default": {"url": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi/HnrnliBuMOU/default.jpg", "width": 120, "height": 90}, "standard": {"url": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi/HnrnliBuMOU/sddefault.jpg", "width": 640, "height": 480}}, "description": "Is the Gospel just ancient history - or is it alive today?\\nIn the premiere episode of Gospel According To, UFC Hall of Famer Bas Rutten shares his powerful testimony - from bullied kid in the Netherlands to becoming one of the most feared fighters in MMA history.\\nThis is not just a sports story.\\nIt’s a story about fear.\\nIdentity.\\nAddiction.\\nSuccess that doesn’t satisfy.\\nAnd the moment everything changed.\\nAfter rising to become the “Baddest Man on the Planet” in Pancrase and the UFC, Bas faced something he couldn’t fight in the ring: loss of identity, injury, and perso