	(45, 2, 'quxX3qnHoDM', 'EWTN - Anticipating Easter', 'ewtn-anticipating-easter', 'Please scan the QR code or visit ewtn.com/eastergiving to make a donation today. Your support keeps EWTN on the air, shares the joy of the Gospel, and helps broadcast news from a Catholic perspective! You may also call 1-800-447-EWTN or send your donation to EWTN, 5817 Old Leeds Rd, Irondale, AL 35210.\n\nSubscribe to EWTN’s YouTube Channel: https://bit.ly/3hBbdVX\n\nEWTN Global Catholic Network, in its 40th year, is the largest religious media network in the world and was founded by Mother Mary Angelica, PCPA. The Daily Televised Mass is broadcast live 7 days a week at 7:00 a.m CST (watch it here: https://www.ewtn.com/tv/watch-live). The Mass is uploaded to YouTube every day along with many other programs. To contact EWTN, send an email to our Viewer Services team at viewer@ewtn.com or call 1-800-447-3986.\n\nTo learn more about EWTN please visit https://www.ewtn.com\nDonate now - https://bit.ly/3pBGjRU\nFollow us on Facebook - https://www.facebook.com/ewtnonline\nFollow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/EWTN\nFollow us on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/ewtnmedia/', 'https://i.ytimg.com/vi/quxX3qnHoDM/hqdefault.jpg', '2026-03-23 04:00:48', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=quxX3qnHoDM', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/quxX3qnHoDM', 'PT1M1S', 998, 0, 20, '{"id": "quxX3qnHoDM", "etag": "lTCCiNcsA7xFc1B_RpK7bkd8Zfc", "kind": "youtube#video", "snippet": {"tags": ["promo", "promo-951303a5e8e66114"], "title": "EWTN - Anticipating Easter", "channelId": "UCijDos-LUTh9RQvSCMQqN6Q", "localized": {"title": "EWTN - Anticipating Easter", "description": "Please scan the QR code or visit ewtn.com/eastergiving to make a donation today. Your support keeps EWTN on the air, shares the joy of the Gospel, and helps broadcast news from a Catholic perspective! You may also call 1-800-447-EWTN or send your donation to EWTN, 5817 Old Leeds Rd, Irondale, AL 35210.\\n\\nSubscribe to EWTN’s YouTube Channel