	(47, 2, 'bz7teJC_GXo', 'When You’re Angry at God — Watch This', 'when-youre-angry-at-god-watch-this', 'What do you do when you’ve suffered… survived… and still feel angry at God?\nIn this deeply emotional moment, a caller shares her struggle after battling cancer—not once, but multiple times. Though she survived, she admits something many are afraid to say out loud:\n\n👉 “I feel angry… and I don’t have peace.”\nMother Angelica responds with honesty, compassion, and truth—reminding us that even in suffering, God understands our weakness, our exhaustion, and our pain.\n\nStay connected with the content you care about. Subscribe to our new EWTN channels and never miss what inspires you.\nEWTN News: https://www.youtube.com/@ewtnnews\nEWTN Live Mass & Devotions: https://www.youtube.com/@EWTNLiveMass\nEWTN On Air: https://www.youtube.com/@EWTNOnAir\nEWTN Radio: https://www.youtube.com/@radioewtn\nEWTN Religious Catalogue: https://www.youtube.com/@EWTNReligiousCatalogue\nEWTN Kids: https://www.youtube.com/@EWTNKids\nEWTN Espanol: https://www.youtube.com/@EWTNespanol\nACI Prensa: https://www.youtube.com/@aciprensa\nFranciscan Missionaries of the Eternal Word: https://www.youtube.com/@MFVAFriars\n\nSupport EWTN:\nhttps://www.ewtn.com/donate\n\nFollow EWTN on Social Media:\n🖥️ Website: https://www.ewtn.com\n📸 Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/ewtnmedia/\n📌 Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/ewtnonline/\n🆇 Twitter/X: https://x.com/EWTN\n📱 TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@ewtnmedia\n\n#motherangelica #ewtn', 'https://i.ytimg.com/vi/bz7teJC_GXo/maxresdefault.jpg', '2026-03-20 17:03:53', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bz7teJC_GXo', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/bz7teJC_GXo', 'PT2M37S', 8971, 0, 22, '{"id": "bz7teJC_GXo", "etag": "Vrt87zBvv2l2dZZiO9Xh6e1SZac", "kind": "youtube#video", "snippet": {"tags": ["mother angelica", "suffering", "god suffering", "catholic", "why does god allow suffering"], "title": "When You’re Angry at God — Watch This", "channelId": "UCijDos-LUTh9R