	(64, 3, '3RwAUwC96bE', 'Responding to Claims that Modesty is for "Controlling Women" w/ Catherine Rose', 'responding-to-claims-that-modesty-is-for-controlling-women-w-catherine-rose', 'More Catholic Answers: https://www.catholic.com\nDonate: https://www.catholicanswersradio.com\nBook a speaker: https://www.catholic.com/speakers\n\nSUBSCRIBE TO CA LIVE CLUB:\nhttps://www.catholic.com/radioclub?email\n\nTopic: A Return to Beauty\nGuest: Catherine Rose\n\nFor more, visit catholic.com\n\n0:00 Intro\n33:33 - How do we consider the different geographic and culture sensitivities to dress when it comes to modesty?  \n40:27 - How can the Church restore a renewed sense of proper and respectful dress at Mass?  \n44:29 - What responsibility do men have when it comes to custody of the eyes?  \n51:45 - At her parish the pastor has instilled a presentable dress code for volunteers during Mass which is setting and example for the congregation.\n\nFor more, visit catholic.com', 'https://i.ytimg.com/vi/3RwAUwC96bE/maxresdefault.jpg', '2026-03-18 11:07:34', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3RwAUwC96bE', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/3RwAUwC96bE', 'PT56M6S', 1859, 0, 15, '{"id": "3RwAUwC96bE", "etag": "vou2nrC7fZkxfqvrpEUHs3T4ey0", "kind": "youtube#video", "snippet": {"title": "Responding to Claims that Modesty is for \\"Controlling Women\\" w/ Catherine Rose", "channelId": "UCvwbLBTkuIwqNm9kHUqWRnw", "localized": {"title": "Responding to Claims that Modesty is for \\"Controlling Women\\" w/ Catherine Rose", "description": "More Catholic Answers: https://www.catholic.com\\nDonate: https://www.catholicanswersradio.com\\nBook a speaker: https://www.catholic.com/speakers\\n\\nSUBSCRIBE TO CA LIVE CLUB:\\nhttps://www.catholic.com/radioclub?email\\n\\nTopic: A Return to Beauty\\nGuest: Catherine Rose\\n\\nFor more, visit catholic.com\\n\\n0:00 Intro\\n33:33 - How do we consider the different geographic and culture sensitivities to dress when it comes to modesty?  \\n40:27 - How can the Ch