	(65, 3, '_6WHceJzy-w', 'Why Are You Pro-Choice? Call us and Debate - @catholicconverts', 'why-are-you-pro-choice-call-us-and-debate-at-catholicconverts', 'More Catholic Answers: https://www.catholic.com\nDonate: https://www.catholicanswersradio.com\nBook a speaker: https://www.catholic.com/speakers\n\nSUBSCRIBE TO CA LIVE CLUB:\nhttps://www.catholic.com/radioclub?email\n\nTopic: Why Are You Pro-Choice? \nGuest: Emily Dinneny \n\nFor more, visit catholic.com\n\n0:00 Intro\n12:54 - Why would we be against wanting to end their own life if they are suffering?  \n21:00 - I was abused growing up and considered assisted suicide and didn’t have the resources necessary to deal with the trauma.  \n32:22 - Is legislation the most grace filled way to protect the unborn?  \n41:18 - What is the Church’s stance on passing legislation that would punish abortion providers and people who procure abortions; should they be punished as murderers?  \n48:32 - What about Father’s who are completely left out of the decision if the child is aborted or not?  \n\nFor more, visit catholic.com', 'https://i.ytimg.com/vi/_6WHceJzy-w/maxresdefault.jpg', '2026-03-18 10:00:04', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_6WHceJzy-w', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/_6WHceJzy-w', 'PT55M3S', 1907, 0, 16, '{"id": "_6WHceJzy-w", "etag": "4IuLwvMtt4m3kAqJhHOJg7QKxVs", "kind": "youtube#video", "snippet": {"title": "Why Are You Pro-Choice? Call us and Debate - @catholicconverts", "channelId": "UCvwbLBTkuIwqNm9kHUqWRnw", "localized": {"title": "Why Are You Pro-Choice? Call us and Debate - @catholicconverts", "description": "More Catholic Answers: https://www.catholic.com\\nDonate: https://www.catholicanswersradio.com\\nBook a speaker: https://www.catholic.com/speakers\\n\\nSUBSCRIBE TO CA LIVE CLUB:\\nhttps://www.catholic.com/radioclub?email\\n\\nTopic: Why Are You Pro-Choice? \\nGuest: Emily Dinneny \\n\\nFor more, visit catholic.com\\n\\n0:00 Intro\\n12:54 - Why would we be against wanting to end their own life if t