	(102, 5, 'Mgxp0tU94xs', 'Fr. Mike Schmitz and Michael Iskander on "House of David", Catholic Faith, and More', 'fr-mike-schmitz-and-michael-iskander-on-house-of-david-catholic-faith-and-more', 'Fr. Mike Schmitz sits down with Michael Iskander, best known for his role as King David in House of David, for a powerful conversation on faith, vocation, and the journey toward God.\n\nThey reflect on David as a flawed man after God’s own heart, exploring what it means to live faithfully, trust God’s mercy, and simply do the “next right thing.”\n\nMichael also shares his journey to Catholicism, including his experience growing up in Egypt amid persecution and the moments that led him to a deeper relationship with God. \n\nMichael also shares his “five stones” for spiritual battle, which serve as a practical and powerful roadmap for staying grounded in the spiritual life: \n\nThe Rosary\nThe Eucharist\nSacred Scripture\nFasting\nMonthly Confession\n\nDon’t miss this inspiring conversation and be sure to check out Season 2 of House of David, streaming March 27 on Prime Video.', 'https://i.ytimg.com/vi/Mgxp0tU94xs/maxresdefault.jpg', '2026-03-25 19:57:30', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Mgxp0tU94xs', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/Mgxp0tU94xs', 'PT36M44S', 25070, 0, 5, '{"id": "Mgxp0tU94xs", "etag": "hR7HuhWQQ7opfOwmdepTJJtHuUM", "kind": "youtube#video", "snippet": {"tags": ["Ascension", "Ascension presents", "Fr. Mike", "Fr. Mike Schmitz", "Michael Iskander", "Father Mike", "Fr. Schmitz", "House of David", "king david", "house of david prime", "amazon prime", "Catholic", "Bible", "Catholicism", "conversion", "religion", "persecution", "michael iskander", "house of david", "the chosen", "jonathan roumie", "christian inspiration", "spiritual journey", "david and goliath", "faith and courage", "biblical drama series", "prime video originals", "house of david season 2", "house of david trailer", "Bible stories"], "title": "Fr. Mike Schmitz and Michael Iskander on \\"House of Da