t right thing.”\\n\\nMichael also shares his journey to Catholicism, including his experience growing up in Egypt amid persecution and the moments that led him to a deeper relationship with God. \\n\\nMichael also shares his “five stones” for spiritual battle, which serve as a practical and powerful roadmap for staying grounded in the spiritual life: \\n\\nThe Rosary\\nThe Eucharist\\nSacred Scripture\\nFasting\\nMonthly Confession\\n\\nDon’t miss this inspiring conversation and be sure to check out Season 2 of House of David, streaming March 27 on Prime Video.", "publishedAt": "2026-03-25T20:57:30Z", "channelTitle": "Ascension Presents", "defaultLanguage": "en", "defaultAudioLanguage": "en-US", "liveBroadcastContent": "none"}, "statistics": {"likeCount": "1688", "viewCount": "25070", "commentCount": "115", "favoriteCount": "0"}, "contentDetails": {"caption": "false", "duration": "PT36M44S", "dimension": "2d", "definition": "hd", "projection": "rectangular", "contentRating": [], "licensedContent": true}}', '2026-03-29 09:21:36', '2026-03-29 09:33:19'),
