	(104, 5, '-zyRoBjXnYQ', 'Do you suffer from the Holy Mass Autopilot Effect? #shorts', 'do-you-suffer-from-the-holy-mass-autopilot-effect-shorts', 'Does your mind wander at Mass? You may be suffering from a  common condition known as the Holy Mass Autopilot Effect! 😵‍💫 \n\nRemedy this familiar ailment with the Pocket Guide to the Mass,  a tiny book with a big impact! \n\nAct now and order yours today: https://AscensionPress.com/Mass #short', 'https://i.ytimg.com/vi/-zyRoBjXnYQ/maxresdefault.jpg', '2026-03-25 15:12:55', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-zyRoBjXnYQ', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/-zyRoBjXnYQ', 'PT1M12S', 83609, 0, 7, '{"id": "-zyRoBjXnYQ", "etag": "b3nf7UawTFlr6LDJ52UYY0JUFW8", "kind": "youtube#video", "snippet": {"title": "Do you suffer from the Holy Mass Autopilot Effect? #shorts", "channelId": "UCVdGX3N-WIJ5nUvklBTNhAw", "localized": {"title": "Do you suffer from the Holy Mass Autopilot Effect? #shorts", "description": "Does your mind wander at Mass? You may be suffering from a  common condition known as the Holy Mass Autopilot Effect! 😵‍💫 \\n\\nRemedy this familiar ailment with the Pocket Guide to the Mass,  a tiny book with a big impact! \\n\\nAct now and order yours today: https://AscensionPress.com/Mass #short"}, "categoryId": "24", "thumbnails": {"high": {"url": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi/-zyRoBjXnYQ/hqdefault.jpg", "width": 480, "height": 360}, "maxres": {"url": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi/-zyRoBjXnYQ/maxresdefault.jpg", "width": 1280, "height": 720}, "medium": {"url": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi/-zyRoBjXnYQ/mqdefault.jpg", "width": 320, "height": 180}, "default": {"url": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi/-zyRoBjXnYQ/default.jpg", "width": 120, "height": 90}, "standard": {"url": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi/-zyRoBjXnYQ/sddefault.jpg", "width": 640, "height": 480}}, "description": "Does your mind wander at Mass? You may be suffering from a  common condition known as the Holy Mass Autopilot Effect! 😵‍💫 \\n\\nRemedy this familiar ailment with the Pocket Guide to the Mass,  a tiny book with a big impact! \\n\\nAct now and order yours today: https://AscensionPress.com/Mass #short", "publishedAt": "2026-03-25T16:12:55Z", "channelTitle": "Ascension Presents", "defaultLanguage": "en", "defaultAudioLanguage": "en", "liveBroadcastContent": "none"}, "statistics": {"likeCount": "6391", "viewCount": "83609", "commentCount": "238", "favoriteCount": "0"}, "contentDetails": {"caption": "false", "duration": "PT1M12S", "dimension": "2d", "definition": "hd", "projection": "rectangular", "contentRating": [], "licensedContent": true}}', '2026-03-29 09:21:36', '2026-03-29 09:33:19'),
	(105, 5, 'VO36r3D5zpc', 'You’re Not Unhappy…You’re Misunderstanding Happiness (w/ Dr. Arthur Brooks and Fr. Mike Schmitz)', 'youre-not-unhappyyoure-misunderstanding-happiness-w-dr-arthur-brooks-and-fr-mike-schmitz', 'Why does life feel empty — even when everything seems “fine”?\n\nFr. Mike Schmitz and Dr. Arthur Brooks, Harvard professor and bestselling author, unpack the real reason so many of us feel restless, anxious, and unfulfilled.\n\nDrawing from both science and the Catholic faith, they explore:\n🔸why pleasure isn’t the same as happiness\n🔸the “arrival fallacy” and why success doesn’t satisfy\n🔸how modern life trains us to avoid waiting\n🔸what it actually means to find lasting joy\n\n✨Join Dr. Arthur Brooks on March 27 for his book launch event with a host of interesting guests. This event is free, virtual, and LIVE! To register and learn more about his new book, go to themeaningofyourlife.com.✨\n\nThe Meaning of Your Life: Finding Purpose in an Age of Emptiness, by Arthur C. Brooks, will be published on March 31. \n\nFrom the #1 New York Times bestselling author of From Strength to Strength, the definitive account of how the modern world makes meaning so hard to find—and a plan to discover your life’s deepest purpose.\n\nIf you struggle to discern life’s meaning, you’re not alone. Millions today describe a growing sense of emptiness, a lack of purpose and significance. And there’s a reason: Rapid cultural, economic, and technological changes have rewired our brains, reducing their ability to perceive depth and purpose.\n\nIn The Meaning of Your Life, social scientist and happiness expert Arthur C. Brooks shows you how to push back against these changes and find the meaning you need to live a happy, fulfilling life. Relying on cutting-edge science, he offers practical, evidence-based strategies for breaking free of the powerful trends and personal habits that dull your focus on the why of your life. Drawing on the great philosophers and the world’s faith traditions, he shows how everyone can—and must—approach life’s most important and mysterious questions and provides a blueprint that will help even the most skeptical person find a life of spiritual transcendence, passionate love, and true calling.\n\n“What is the meaning of my life?” is not an unanswerable question, but rather the start of a pilgrimage into unexplored corners of your consciousness. The Meaning of Your Life is your handbook for this journey.\n\n—  MORE FROM ASCENSION  —\n🔸Ascension App: https://link.ascension-app.com/lMuydd... \n🔸The Great Adventure Bible: https://tinyurl.com/y6lfxzyt\n🔸 Catechism of the Catholic Church, Ascension Edition: https://tinyurl.com/25nskztb\n—  SOCIAL MEDIA  —\n🔸Facebook:   / ascensionpress  \n🔸Twitter:   / ascensionpress  \n🔸LinkedIn:    / ascension-press  \n🔸Instagram:   / ascensionpress', 'https://i.ytimg.com/vi/VO36r3D5zpc/maxresdefault.jpg', '2026-03-24 16:30:13', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VO36r3D5zpc', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/VO36r3D5zpc', 'PT38M23S', 51983, 0, 8, '{"id": "VO36r3D5zpc", "etag": "P-Ut215yb-7e34Te5nXbuqaiz4w", "kind": "youtube#video", "snippet": {"tags": ["Ascesnion", "Ascension presents", "Ascension press", "Arthur Brooks", "Fr. Mike Schmitz", "Fr. Mike", "Father Mike", "empty", "happy", "lonely", "sad", "sadness", "depression", "life", "life feels empty", "depressed", "meaning of life", "what\'s the meaning of life", "Mike Schmitz", "Catholic", "Dr. Brooks", "Dr. Arthur Brooks", "Fr. Mike and Arthur Brooks", "Catholic Church", "social media", "instagram", "scroll", "happiness", "ascension presents fr mike schmitz"], "title": "You’re Not Unhappy…You’re Misunderstanding Happiness (w/ Dr. Arthur Brooks and Fr. Mike Schmitz)", "channelId": "UCVdGX3N-WIJ5nUvklBTNhAw", "localized": {"title": "You’re Not Unhappy…You’re Misunderstanding Happiness (w/ Dr. Arthur Brooks and Fr. Mike Schmitz)", "description": "Why does life feel empty — even when everything seems “fine”?\\n\\nFr. Mike Schmitz and D