	(107, 5, 'kd34HqFiNf0', 'The Lie Modern Men Keep Believing (w/ Fr. Mark-Mary Ames)', 'the-lie-modern-men-keep-believing-w-fr-mark-mary-ames', 'What matters more than looking good and feeling good is that we are in fact good. How are our daily choices impacting the people we become?\n\nFr. Mark-Mary challenges us to take an honest look at what holds our attention and what might be quietly capturing our hearts. Without awareness, our daily habits can pull us away from virtue. The invitation is to engage what we love in a way that actually forms us into better people, not weaker ones.\n\nLet God lead you this Lent! Sign up for your most powerful Lent experience today! https://ascensionpress.com/pages/crux\n\n❓ Have ideas for future videos ❓ Topics you want to hear about ❓ Questions you want answered ❓ Make sure to put #AskAscension in your comment  👍\n\n—  MORE FROM ASCENSION  —\n\n🔸Ascension App: https://link.ascension-app.com/lMuydd... \n🔸The Great Adventure Bible: https://tinyurl.com/y6lfxzyt\n🔸 Catechism of the Catholic Church, Ascension Edition: https://tinyurl.com/25nskztb\n\n—  SOCIAL MEDIA  —\n\n🔸Facebook:   / ascensionpress  \n🔸Twitter:   / ascensionpress  \n🔸LinkedIn:    / ascension-press  \n🔸Instagram:   / ascensionpress  \n🔸Subscribe:   @AscensionPresents\n\n11388538501', 'https://i.ytimg.com/vi/kd34HqFiNf0/maxresdefault.jpg', '2026-03-23 15:38:52', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kd34HqFiNf0', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/kd34HqFiNf0', 'PT8M33S', 28346, 0, 10, '{"id": "kd34HqFiNf0", "etag": "e73vEUuhq81LIak6bI9NHsCMrh0", "kind": "youtube#video", "snippet": {"tags": ["Ascension", "Ascension presents", "Fr. Mark-Mary", "CFR", "CFRs", "guys", "lent", "fast", "working out", "gambling", "porn", "pornography", "virtue", "vice", "sin", "church", "the Church", "the Catholic Church", "St. Joseph", "Joseph", "saint", "st. joseph", "heaven", "God", "Jesus", "Jesus Christ"], "title": "The Lie Modern Men Keep Believing (w/ Fr. Mark-Mary Ames)", "channelId": "UCVdGX