	(112, 5, '2CCchV64AvU', 'I Forgave Them...So Why Am I Still Mad? (w/ Fr. Rob Mulderink)', 'i-forgave-themso-why-am-i-still-mad-w-fr-rob-mulderink', 'Forgiveness isn’t always a feeling. So what does it mean if you’re still angry?\n\nIn this video, Fr. Rob Mulderink unpacks what true forgiveness really is—and how to know if you’ve actually forgiven, even when the hurt hasn’t gone away.\n\nIf you’ve ever wondered, “Have I really forgiven?” this video is for you.\n\nLet God lead you this Lent! Sign up for your most powerful Lent experience today! https://ascensionpress.com/pages/crux\n\n❓ Have ideas for future videos ❓ Topics you want to hear about ❓ Questions you want answered ❓ Make sure to put #AskAscension in your comment  👍\n\n—  MORE FROM ASCENSION  —\n\n🔸Ascension App: https://link.ascension-app.com/lMuyddWAqHb \n🔸The Great Adventure Bible: https://tinyurl.com/y6lfxzyt\n🔸 Catechism of the Catholic Church, Ascension Edition: https://tinyurl.com/25nskztb\n\n—  SOCIAL MEDIA  —\n\n🔸Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/AscensionPress/\n🔸Twitter: http://twitter.com/AscensionPress\n🔸LinkedIn:  https://www.linkedin.com/company/ascension-press\n🔸Instagram: http://www.instagram.com/ascensionpress/\n🔸Subscribe:   @AscensionPresents    \n\n—  BULLDOG CATHOLIC  —\n\n🔸YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCXzB400_Skw95z2TmAsSkIg\n🔸iTunes: https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/umd-newman-catholic-campus-ministry/id273537688', 'https://i.ytimg.com/vi/2CCchV64AvU/maxresdefault.jpg', '2026-03-20 16:30:00', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2CCchV64AvU', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/2CCchV64AvU', 'PT5M38S', 42030, 0, 15, '{"id": "2CCchV64AvU", "etag": "xIiXj3W4Cdy7PGFhP-OeTeF_7V4", "kind": "youtube#video", "snippet": {"title": "I Forgave Them...So Why Am I Still Mad? (w/ Fr. Rob Mulderink)", "channelId": "UCVdGX3N-WIJ5nUvklBTNhAw", "localized": {"title": "I Forgave Them...So Why Am I Still Mad? (w/ Fr. Rob Mulderink)", "description": "Forgiveness isn’t always a feeling. So what