	(139, 6, 'Agu8XptlX38', 'A Catholic Convert\'s Guide to the Liturgy of the Hours', 'a-catholic-converts-guide-to-the-liturgy-of-the-hours', 'Have you ever thought about praying the Liturgy of the Hours, but weren\'t sure how to begin?\n\nJonMarc Grodi of the Coming Home Network is joined by Nathan Wigfield from the Saint Thomas More House of Prayer to give a brief overview of the Divine Office, how it works, and why it\'s such a beloved tradition in the life of the Church.\n\nThey also give a demonstration of Vespers (Evening Prayer) so that you can get a sense of the mechanics of the Breviary.\n\nIf you\'re a Catholic convert, or someone exploring the Catholic Faith, and are interested in praying the Liturgy of the Hours, we hope you find this discussion helpful!\n\nMore about the Saint Thomas More House of Prayer: https://www.liturgyofthehours.org\n\nThe Coming Home Network was established to help inquiring clergy and laity of various faiths -- or even no faith at all -- with fellowship, resources, and encouragement as they explore the possibility of becoming Catholic.\n\nFind out more about our work: https://www.chnetwork.org\n\nJoin our FREE Online Community: https://community.chnetwork.org\n\nFacebook: https://www.facebook.com/CHNetwork\nTwitter: https://twitter.com/chnetwork\nInstagram: https://www.instagram.com/cominghomenetwork\n\nSupport our mission: https://www.chnetwork.org/compass', 'https://i.ytimg.com/vi/Agu8XptlX38/maxresdefault.jpg', '2026-01-27 20:07:57', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Agu8XptlX38', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/Agu8XptlX38', 'PT24M1S', 781, 0, 18, '{"id": "Agu8XptlX38", "etag": "2ZbYVGfh3wpD5335nc8IhGWoxds", "kind": "youtube#video", "snippet": {"tags": ["God", "Jesus", "Holy Spirit", "Faith", "Religion", "Spirituality", "Prayer", "Becoming Catholic", "Catholic Prayer", "How to become Catholic", "Protestant to Catholic", "How to Pray", "Prayer resources", "Prayer guides", "Evangelical to Catholic", "Atheist to Catholic", "Liturg