	(141, 6, 'XJe8W-tGso8', 'Jesus told his followers to obey the Pharisees. Why? - Dr. Brant Pitre', 'jesus-told-his-followers-to-obey-the-pharisees-why-dr-brant-pitre', 'In this excerpt from the 2009 Deep in History conference, Dr. Brant Pitre explains why Jesus tells his hearers in Matthew 23 why they should obey the Pharisees. Dr. Pitre also discusses what this shows us about the nature of true authority, and why Jesus set up the Church in the way that He did.\n\nWatch the full talk: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xl3pD4l0K5U\n\nThe Coming Home Network was established to help inquiring clergy and laity of various faiths -- or even no faith at all -- with fellowship, resources, and encouragement as they explore the possibility of becoming Catholic.\n\nFind out more about our work: https://www.chnetwork.org\n\nJoin our FREE Online Community: https://community.chnetwork.org\n\nFacebook: https://www.facebook.com/CHNetwork\nTwitter: https://twitter.com/chnetwork\nInstagram: https://www.instagram.com/cominghomenetwork\n\nSupport our mission: https://www.chnetwork.org/compass', 'https://i.ytimg.com/vi/XJe8W-tGso8/maxresdefault.jpg', '2026-01-21 19:13:54', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XJe8W-tGso8', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/XJe8W-tGso8', 'PT2M49S', 854, 0, 20, '{"id": "XJe8W-tGso8", "etag": "xEkS6dl8g4-hPRssc2gC5iZTSSA", "kind": "youtube#video", "snippet": {"tags": ["Papacy", "Jesus and the Jewish Roots of the Eucharist", "Jesus and the Jewish Roots of Mary", "Catholic Apologetics", "Biblical Apologetics", "Catholic Convert", "Becoming Catholic", "Catholic History", "Church History", "Bishop Barron", "Scott Hahn", "The Journey home", "Pastors Becoming Catholic", "EWTN", "the Chosen", "Matthew 16:18", "Is Peter the Rock", "Fr. Mike Schmitz"], "title": "Jesus told his followers to obey the Pharisees. Why? - Dr. Brant Pitre", "channelId": "UCIDebJFlV5aIsFs2jzxASrQ", "localized": {"title": "Jesus told his followers to obey the Pharisees. Why? - Dr. Brant Pitre", "des