	(142, 6, 'kJpFtn63o7U', 'How Do We Know Matthew\'s Gospel Is Inspired? - OTJ Short', 'how-do-we-know-matthews-gospel-is-inspired-otj-short', 'Christians believe the Bible is the inspired Word of God. But how do we know that all the books in it truly belong there?\n\nKen Hensley shares how his experience as a Baptist pastor led him to realize that in order for him to preach effectively to his congregation, he had to be able to articulate on what basis the Bible he was preaching from was truly inspired by God.\n\nWatch the full episode: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bx8N_w_WD90\n\nThe Coming Home Network was established to help inquiring clergy and laity of various faiths -- or even no faith at all -- with fellowship, resources, and encouragement as they explore the possibility of becoming Catholic.\n\nFind out more about our work: https://www.chnetwork.org\n\nJoin our FREE Online Community: https://community.chnetwork.org\n\nFacebook: https://www.facebook.com/CHNetwork\nTwitter: https://twitter.com/chnetwork\nInstagram: https://www.instagram.com/cominghomenetwork\n\nSupport our mission: https://www.chnetwork.org/compass', 'https://i.ytimg.com/vi/kJpFtn63o7U/maxresdefault.jpg', '2026-01-21 13:55:52', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kJpFtn63o7U', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/kJpFtn63o7U', 'PT3M7S', 567, 0, 21, '{"id": "kJpFtn63o7U", "etag": "4vXD-qINuQ737ciPTtyDBsVV6z4", "kind": "youtube#video", "snippet": {"tags": ["Jesus", "Holy Spirit", "Faith", "Spirituality", "Prayer", "Becoming Catholic", "Pastors becoming Catholic", "Sola Scriptura", "Bible alone", "Baptist to Catholic", "Foursquare to Catholic", "Evangelical to Catholic", "Pentecostal to Catholic", "Free Methodist to Catholic", "Wesleyan to Catholic", "Reformed to Catholic", "Early Church", "Church history", "Christian history", "Nicene Creed", "Apostles Creed", "Journey Home", "EWTN", "Catholic Answers", "Bishop Barron", "Apologetics", "Scriptural Apologetics", "Catholic vs Protestant"], "title": "How Do